rows.label: qst200917_msg001
rows.name: Kupon-san! We got your cargo back!

rows.label: qst200917_msg003
rows.name:
Yup! And as I expected, it
was a piece of cake for us
as we are right now!

rows.label: qst200917_msg004
rows.name:
Probably about time we
head to Tilly Bakery now?

rows.label: qst200917_msg005
rows.name:
No! Not going with Kasane,
not even if Cloud Sea freeze
over! Kupon go on ahead!

rows.label: qst200917_msg007
rows.name: I wonder why he was in such a hurry?

rows.label: qst200917_msg008
rows.name:
Hey, if I were in his position,
I'd probably do the same.

rows.label: qst200917_msg010
rows.name:
In any case, we should
head back to Torigo now.
